Ms. Ko and I are best friends now.

308
00:22:21,848 --> 00:22:25,268
That means we're buddies and besties.
It means we're really close.

309
00:22:25,351 --> 00:22:29,147
Your best friend is Jae-su.
My best friend is Ms. Ko.

310
