to the psychiatric hospital tomorrow.

599
00:40:21,843 --> 00:40:23,303
I mean, look at those eyes.

600
00:40:23,595 --> 00:40:25,305
Do you think they can be apart?

601
00:40:28,183 --> 00:40:31,728
