616
00:41:41,757 --> 00:41:44,843
-Well, he'll get here pretty late.
-Did he get a part-time job again?

617
00:41:44,926 --> 00:41:46,595
No, he had to meet someone.

618
00:41:46,678 --> 00:41:47,512
