746
00:50:33,612 --> 00:50:36,323
Hey. Shall we

747
00:50:36,407 --> 00:50:39,201
become friends?

748
00:50:45,332 --> 00:50:47,376
<i>I liked it because I was no longer bored.</i>

749
00:50:48,335 --> 00:50:49,253
<i>And she liked it</i>

750
00:50:49,545 --> 00:50:52,047
